DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: Any material sample taken from a biological entity for testing, diagnostic, propagation, treatment or research purposes, including a sample obtained from a living organism or taken from the biological object after halting of all its life functions. ValueMeaning.preferredDefinition: A text-based format for storing a biological sequence that encodes the nucleotide calls as well as their quality scores.

Concepts.definition: A text-based format for storing a biological sequence that encodes the nucleotide calls as well as their quality scores. It is an extension of the FASTA format.
